function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	for i, idPlayer in pairs(Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()) do
		if isPlayerInExterior(idPlayer) then
			Hydra.ActorPlayDisembodiedConversation(conv_Neyrelle_01, idPlayer)
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(conv_Neyrelle_01)
	
	for i, idPlayer in pairs(Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()) do
		if isPlayerInExterior(idPlayer) then
			Hydra.ActorPlayDisembodiedConversation(conv_Neyrelle_02, idPlayer)
		end
	end
end

local function isPlayerInExterior(idPlayer)
	return Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPlayer) 
--		and 
--		( Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idPlayer) == levelarea_HoradricExterior or  
--		Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idPlayer) == levelarea_MistralWoods or
--		Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idPlayer) == levelarea_GaleValley)
end

local function isPlayerInInterior(idPlayer)
	return Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPlayer) 
--	and Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idPlayer) == levelarea_Horadric_Interior
end
